WEBVTT

00:03.471 --> 00:05.739
GEORGE, LOOK AT US.
WE'RE THE NEIGHBORHOOD WATCH,

00:05.739 --> 00:08.442
AND YOU'VE GOT US
DRESSED LIKE CRIMINALS.

00:08.442 --> 00:11.045
THE SAFETY VIDEO SAID
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO WEAR

00:11.045 --> 00:13.047
OUR REFLECTOR VESTS.

00:13.047 --> 00:14.848
ANGIE, WE HAVE
THE ELEMENT OF SURPRISE.

00:14.848 --> 00:18.886
97% OF ALL ARRESTS ARE MADE
BY UNDERCOVER COPS.

00:18.886 --> 00:21.289
OKAY, THE VEST
WAS TOO SMALL.

00:21.289 --> 00:24.024
MY HEAD DIDN'T FIT
THROUGH THE NECK HOLE.

00:24.024 --> 00:26.794
