WE'RE NOT EVEN ARMED.

00:26.794 --> 00:30.331
I DON'T NEED TO BE ARMED.
MY BODY IS MY WEAPON. WHAT-TCHA.

00:30.331 --> 00:32.700
I DON'T WANNA HEAR

00:32.700 --> 00:35.869
ABOUT YOUR TWO WEEKS
OF JUDO AT THE "Y" AGAIN.

00:35.869 --> 00:40.007
YOU DON'T THINK I KNOW
WHAT I'M DOING? GRAB MY SHIRT.

00:40.007 --> 00:42.910
I'M NOT GONNA
GRAB YOUR SHIRT.

00:42.910 --> 00:46.947
GO AHEAD, GRAB IT.
WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF, PUNK?

00:46.947 --> 00:48.616
FINE.

00:49.950 --> 00:51.919
NOT AT THE BOTTOM.

00:51.919 --> 00:53.921
WHO GRABS A SHIRT
AT THE BOTTOM?

00:53.921 --> 00:55.923
GRAB IT LIKE
YOU WANNA KILL ME.

00:55.923 --> 00:57.758
THAT I CAN DO.

00:57.758 --> 01:01.028
YOU'RE STILL NOT GETTING IT.
HERE, LET ME SHOW YOU.

01:01.028 --> 01:03.197
